init_text: Humans once wielded formidable magical power. But with over 7 billion of us on the planet now, Mana has spread far too thinly to have any effect. When hostile aliens reduce humanity to a mere fraction, the survivors discover an old power has begun to reawaken once again.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: It was the only thing that could have saved you.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The survivors have begun to find that they have the ability to manipulate the energy that the aliens had been using to attack them.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The witches were the only ones who had the power to do it, and they were the only ones who survived.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The witches had discovered that they could manipulate the Earth's magical energies, and they had begun to do so.

actions.text: You can't help but wonder if this is what the old professor had meant.
